@startuml
title Viaverse Locale Resolution / Rendering — Activity Diagram
start
:Screen/page/request;
:Read profile locale;
:Read device/browser locale;
:Read route/country SEO locale;
:Resolve effective locale;
if (Supported?) then (yes)
else (no)
  :Apply fallback chain\ntr-TR → tr → en;
endif
:Load translation bundle\nand regional config;
:Format money/date/unit;
:Render UI/content;
if (SEO page?) then (yes)
  :Canonical/hreflang/schema;
endif
if (Notification?) then (yes)
  :Localized template;
endif
:Track missing keys\nquality event if needed;
:Cache locale assets;
stop

note bottom
Missing translation must not break the app.
It falls back visibly in logs/quality metrics, not silently forever.
end note
@enduml
